select QueueNameOut from lookup where BreweryCode=#[flowVars.BreweryCode]

SELECT S.WB_TRANSFORMATION,S.WB_VALIDATION,S.WB_ENRICHMENT,S.CUSTOM_TRANSFORMATION,S.CUSTOM_VALIDATION,S.CUSTOM_ENRICHMENT,S.PARTNER_NAME FROM WBUSR.TBL_SENDER_MASTER S WHERE S.INTERFACE_ID=#[flowVars['InterfaceID']]
select distinct INTERFACE_ID from SYS.TBL_TRANSPORTS where INPUT_DESTINATION=#[flowVars.InputQueue]
select distinct INTERFACE_ID from ${DataBaseUser}.TBL_TRANSPORTS where INPUT_DESTINATION=#[flowVars.InputQueue]

SELECT R.WB_TRANSFORMATION,R.WB_VALIDATION,R.WB_ENRICHMENT,R.CUSTOM_TRANSFORMATION,R.CUSTOM_VALIDATION,R.CUSTOM_ENRICHMENT,R.PARTNER_NAME,T.OUTPUT_DESTINATION FROM WBUSR.TBL_RECEIVER_MASTER R JOIN WBUSR.TBL_TRANSPORTS T ON (R.INTERFACE_ID=#[flowVars['InterfaceID']] AND T.INTERFACE_ID=#[flowVars['InterfaceID']])
